{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.520", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.240", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.120", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Besucher auf den Trib\u00fcnen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.360", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der hier vorgelegte Haushaltsentwurf l\u00e4sst den Mittelstand im Regen stehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.320", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung aber sonnt sich in einer vermeintlich guten Wirtschaftslage mit hohen Wachstumszahlen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.520", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und weil die Bundesregierung so sehr mit Sonnen besch\u00e4ftigt ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.120", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "tut sie nichts. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.160", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nichts von dem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.960", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was f\u00fcr den Mittelstand wichtig ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.440", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich B\u00fcrokratieabbau, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.280", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fachkr\u00e4ftemangel und digitaler Wandel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.080", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird wirklich ernsthaft angegangen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.200", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr gro\u00df angek\u00fcndigtes Nationales Reformprogramm verspricht \u201eklare Priorit\u00e4ten f\u00fcr Investitionen in Infrastruktur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Vernetzungs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.080", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Digitalisierungsstrategien sowie in Bildung und Forschung\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.720", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Versprechen sind Sie immer spitze. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.240", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind seit Jahren an der Regierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.880", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nichts ist passiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.520", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und jetzt soll alles anders werden? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.080", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr vorgelegter Haushalt spricht eine andere Sprache."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.240", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "W\u00e4hrend beinahe 140\u00a0Milliarden Euro f\u00fcr soziale Wohltaten ausgegeben werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.080", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bleiben dem Mittelstand nur Kleckerbetr\u00e4ge. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.000", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Magere 420\u00a0Millionen Euro umfasst Ihre Digitale Agenda im Wirtschaftsbereich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.680", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "davon entfallen ganze 60\u00a0Millionen Euro auf die F\u00f6rderung der Entwicklung digitaler Technologien. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.520", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und das soll eine Priorit\u00e4t sein?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.520", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur 27\u00a0Millionen Euro stellen Sie f\u00fcr die Sicherung von Fachkr\u00e4ften f\u00fcr kleine und mittlere Unternehmen zur Verf\u00fcgung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.880", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ist das Ihr Ernst? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.920", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind es doch immer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.640", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die \u00fcber den Fachkr\u00e4ftemangel jammern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.080", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Sie wollen der deutschen Bev\u00f6lkerung doch immer einreden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.760", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir die ach so qualifizierten Zuwanderer aus Nordafrika brauchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.440", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie versuchen erst gar nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere eigenen j\u00e4hrlich massenhaft auswandernden deutschen Fachkr\u00e4fte zu halten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.680", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr Nationales Reformprogramm ist Schall und Rauch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.440", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Gro\u00dfteil Ihrer Mittelstands- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.560", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Strukturf\u00f6rderung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.200", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich 43\u00a0Prozent der GRW-Mittel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.720", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kommt in den strukturschwachen Regionen gar nicht erst an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Kaputtsparen der Kommunen hat auch nach Ansicht des Deutschen Instituts f\u00fcr Wirtschaftsforschung dazu gef\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.160", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass kaum noch ein Verwaltungsmitarbeiter da ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.400", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der F\u00f6rdermittel auskehrt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.240", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sollte da doch noch jemand in den verwaisten Amtsstuben sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.440", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann \u00fcbersch\u00fcttet er den Mittelst\u00e4ndler mit Papierkram und Auflagen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.200", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen endlich Geld in die Hand nehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.960", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Laut allen Steuersch\u00e4tzungen ist doch genug Geld da. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.360", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen mehr Geld in die Hand nehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.800", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Rahmenbedingungen zu schaffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.720", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zum Investieren anreizen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit es \u00fcberhaupt etwas zu f\u00f6rdern gibt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.680", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weniger Steuern f\u00fcr kleine und mittelst\u00e4ndische Unternehmen und mehr Luft zum Atmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.960", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das w\u00e4re ehrliche Mittelstandspolitik."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.760", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Minister, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.120", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schauen Sie mal nach \u00d6sterreich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.160", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort werden den Unternehmern die Kosten f\u00fcr Forschung einfach und unb\u00fcrokratisch von der Steuerschuld abgezogen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.960", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das kostet \u00d6sterreich wenig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.760", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bringt aber viel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.160", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich jede Menge Forschungsinvestitionen deutscher Unternehmen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.280", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "allerdings nicht hier, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.240", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern in \u00d6sterreich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.840", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.400", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Mittelstand kommt mit diesem Haushalt vom Regen in die Traufe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.520", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und was macht der Wirtschaftsminister? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.520", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er tingelt von Land zu Land und will die Welt retten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.440", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der deutsche Mittelstand muss leider warten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.600", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit Ihrem vorgespielten Macher-Image, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.360", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Minister, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.480", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist das nicht zu vereinbaren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.080", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie lassen unseren deutschen Mittelstand im Stich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.080", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht mit uns!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.240", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.160", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chste Rednerin: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.000", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sabine Poschmann f\u00fcr die SPD-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}